"    Public awareness of thalassemia",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\">",
"    <table cellspacing=\"0\">",
"     <tbody>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        93 percent were aware of thalassemia",
"       </td>",
